{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Limit penalty charge notices (PCNs) for traffic offences to \u00a320",
        "additional_details": "We believe many PCNs are too expensive, and can amount to a person's entire daily. This is especially unfair for minor offences. Therefore, all PCNs should be restricted to a maximum of \u00a320.\r\n \r\nAs inflation rises and economic conditions worsen, limiting fines like this should help reduce the financial burden on people who are already struggling to make ends meet.\r\n",
        "background": "We want all PCNs that local authorities are able to issue for traffic offences to be limited to \u00a320.",
